\midrule
Natural (baseline) & 2,009 & 0\% & 29/30 (96.7\%) \\
TSCG-only & 189 & 90.6\% & 28/30 (93.3\%) \\
LLMLingua-2 only & 791 & 60.6\% & 24/30 (80.0\%) \\
